[ProMED thanks Dr. Orabi for submitting this report on measles in Aleppo, Syria.

Most likely the fatal case was due to lack of immunity due to incomplete or lack of vaccination but could be due to a change in the virus as suggested in the report. However, if that were the case, one would expect to see more than one severe case. It appears sequencing is being conducted, which will answer that question. We look forward to hearing more about this soon. - Mod.LK

